quran[8{c,v,t}:
35,31,aur yeh kitaab jo hum ne tumhari taraf bhaije hai brhq hai. aur un ( kitabon ) ki tasdeeq karti hai jo is se pehlay ki hain. be shak khuda apne bundon se khabardaar ( aur un ko ) dekhnay wala hai
35,32,phir hum ne un logon ko kitaab ka waris tehraya jin ko apne bundon mein se bargzidakiya. to kuch to un mein se apne aap par zulm karte hain. aur kuch miyana ro hain. aur kuch khuda ke hukum se nakiyon mein agay nikal jaane walay hain. yahi bara fazl hai
35,33,( un logon ke liye ) bahisht javedani ( hain ) jin mein woh daakhil hon ge. wahan un ko sonay ke kangon aur moti pahnaye jayen ge. aur un ki poshak reshmi hogi
35,34,woh kahin ge ke khuda ka shukar hai jis ne hum se gham daurkiya. be shak hamara perwar-digaar bakhsnay wala ( aur ) qadar daan hai
35,35,jis ne hum ko apne fazl se hamesha ke rehne ke ghar mein utaara. yahan nah to hum ko ranj puhanche ga aur nah hamein takan hi hogi
35,36,aur jin logon ne kufarkiya un ke liye dozakh ki aag hai. nah inhen mout aeye gi ke mrjayin aur nah un ka azaab hi un se halkakiya jaye ga. hum har aik nashukray ko aisa hi badla diya karte hain
35,37,woh is mein chalayein ge ke ae perwar-digaar hum ko nikaal le ( ab ) hum naik amalkiya karen ge. nah woh jo ( pehlay ) karte they.kiya hum ne tum ko itni Umar nahi di thi ke is mein jo sochna chahta soch laita aur tumahray paas darane wala bhi aaya. to ab mazay chako. zaalmon ka koi madadgaar nahi
35,38,be shak khuda hi asmano aur zameen ki posheeda baton ka jan-nay wala hai. woh to dil ke bheidoon taq se waaqif hai
